metadata.name: Checkers #1
metadata.description:
Checkers: Checks/Ringers.

Inspired by Ringers by Dmitri Cherniak & Checks by Jack Butcher.

To claim a token, one must offer the Checkers contract a certain quantity of Dead Ringers: Edition by Dmitri Cherniak. Checkers tokens are fully returnable in the contract for the original amount of Dead Ringers Editions initially offered.

• Checkers #1 ― 1 × Dead Ringers Edition

• Checkers #2 ― 2 × Dead Ringers Edition

• Checkers #3 ― 5 × Dead Ringers Edition

• Checkers #4 ― 10 × Dead Ringers Edition

• Checkers #5 ― 20 × Dead Ringers Edition
